{"tid":1841761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"救護員：依家有啲叫救護車嘅人都好「鬼」下，去到醫院先話去過疫區","createTime":"2020-01-25T11:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:59:56.000Z","uid":17332,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93d9cc3fc6859ac4c422224bca2b51227f390aa2","tid":1841761,"uid":17332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/358172207958953/posts/828437510932418/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F358172207958953%2Fposts%2F828437510932418%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FQ2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=be54afaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/358172207958953/posts/828437510932418/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n今日 #年初一 有個著制服嘅救護員哥哥黎睇上呼吸道感染，佢睇咗普通科兩次都未好返，仲好似開始發燒咁，當當下更頂唔順，所以好擔心要黎醫院做詳細檢查。<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢嘅情況並未符合 #疑似武漢肺炎 ，不過佢作為最前線嘅醫護人員，我都戥佢牙煙。<br />\n<br />\n佢話：「依家有啲叫救護車嘅人都好「鬼」下，上咗車一粒聲都唔出，去到醫院先話自己去過高危地方。」<br />\n<br />\n最後檢驗結果無大礙，咁我諗住俾病假俾師兄休息下啦，點知佢話要到診紙就夠，因為人手不足，睇完病就要出返去應call。。。<br />\n<br />\n當大家擔心喺醫院診所嘅醫護嘅時候，請大家唔好忘記 #緊守崗位 #克盡己任 嘅 #救護員！<br />\n<br />\n#dogtor<br />\n圖：星島日報<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WYT22vr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWYT22vr.jpg&h=d7d60505&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aea75e2c9031958ab3d8cedf62f0d8ed01b1f6b","tid":1841761,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":25,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"救護又係返工返到上腦，身價賤撚過奴隸都唔會反抗"},{"pid":"36dded08b2d2f984b6fbddd4372af9a932c0b274","tid":1841761,"uid":69159,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6aea75e2c9031958ab3d8cedf62f0d8ed01b1f6b","tid":1841761,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":25,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"救護又係返工返到上腦，身價賤撚過奴隸都唔會反抗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"食屎啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd68c9800dabf21b43af1f8b637f1aacbb984a9","tid":18417